  "description": "After a terrorist-engineered virus crippled the world, humanity adapted the only way it could — on wheels. Now, survivors roll into battle in high-powered wheelchairs, armed to the teeth and ready to reclaim what’s left.\n\nCustomize your rig, perfect your aim in the gun range, and prepare for fast-paced, tactical wheelchair warfare against players and bots across diverse maps and intense game modes.\n\nGame Modes:• Team Deathmatch – Roll out with your squad and dominate the opposition.\n\n• Free For All – Everyone’s your enemy. Be the last one rolling.\n\n• Gun Game – Earn new weapons with every kill — no breaks, no mercy.\n\n• Last Man Standing – One life. One shot at glory.\n\n• Last Team Standing – Team up, no respawns. Win or get wiped out.\n\nJoin our community, share your feedback, and help shape the future of Wheels of Duty",
  "description_short": "After a deadly virus left humanity paralyzed, survivors now battle on wheels! Customize your rig, sharpen your aim, and roll into fast-paced wheelchair warfare across multiple maps and modes. Join the fight!",
